---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout title="The Book - Pharus Lee" lang={lang}>
  <article class="mx-auto px-6 py-16" style={`max-width: var(--page-max)`}>
    <div class="mx-auto" style={`max-width: var(--prose-width)`}>
      <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-4" style={`color: var(--color-sea-green)`}>
        Book
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold mb-4" style={`font-family: var(--font-serif); line-height: 1.2`}>
        A Soul's Guidebook for the<br />Coming Cosmic Awakening
      </h1>
      <p class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm mb-6" style={`background: var(--color-pale-blue-light); color: var(--color-sea-green); font-weight: 500`}>
        Coming Soon
      </p>

      <div class="my-12 p-8 rounded-xl" style={`background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light)`}>
        <blockquote class="text-lg italic" style={`color: var(--color-ink-muted); font-family: var(--font-serif); line-height: 1.8`}>
          "What we call reality is a stage that consciousness created to experience itself.
          And you are not the audience &mdash; you are the actor, the director, and the theater itself."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          This book begins with the nature of consciousness and unfolds across ten chapters:
          the evolutionary journey of the soul, the interface between DNA and consciousness,
          the sacred dance of polarity beyond dualistic illusion, multidimensional experiences of memory and dreams,
          and the new chapter of consciousness evolution that technology and AI are opening.
        </p>

        <h2>Chapters</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>The Nature of Consciousness and Reality</li>
          <li>The Evolutionary Journey of the Soul</li>
          <li>Soul and DNA &mdash; The Interface of Consciousness and Biology</li>
          <li>The Sacred Dance of Polarity &mdash; Beyond Dualistic Illusion</li>
          <li>Memory, Dreams, and Multidimensional Experience</li>
          <li>The Source of Imagination &mdash; Fantasy as Inter-dimensional Memory</li>
          <li>Prophets, Angels, and Demons</li>
          <li>Technology, AI, and the Evolution of Consciousness</li>
          <li>Interspecies Consciousness and the Cosmic Community</li>
          <li>The Cosmic Role-Play &mdash; Understanding Lila</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
